<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<book>
    <page>
        <scene id="scene1">
            <model id="univers" path="models/univers.glb">
                <scale xyz="3"/>
            </model>
            <model id="petitPrincePlanet" path="models/petit_prince_planet.glb" visible="false">
                <scale xyz="1"/>
                <position y="0.05"/>
            </model>
            <model id="avion" path="models/avion.glb" autoAnimate="false" visible="false">
                <scale xyz="1"/>
                <position y="0.05"/>
                <rotation y="90"/>
            </model>
            <model id="soleil" path="models/soleil.glb" visible="false">
                <scale xyz="0.5"/>
                <position y="0.8" z="0.5"/>
                <rotation y="90"/>
            </model>

            <action id="show_planet">
                <changeVisibility target="petitPrincePlanet" visible="true"/>
            </action>
            <action id="show_soleil">
                <changeVisibility target="soleil" visible="true"/>
            </action>
            <action id="animate_move_avion">
                <animateAll target="avion"/>
                <smoothPosition target="avion" y="0.06" z="1"/>
            </action>
            <action id="hide_planet_show_avion">
                <changeVisibility target="petitPrincePlanet" visible="false"/>
                <changeVisibility target="avion" visible="true"/>
            </action>
 


        </scene>
        <content>
            The little prince's planet was so small that he was bored to death. <keyword action="show_planet">In his world</keyword>, nothing was unknown to him.
            In just ten minutes, he was already walking around it, then sitting down to gaze at the <keyword action="show_soleil">bright sun</keyword> and the other planets in the distance.
            One day he decided to explore the rest of the universe. He took <keyword action="hide_planet_show_avion">his plane</keyword> and <keyword action="animate_move_avion">started the trip</keyword>.
        </content>
    </page>
</book>